Description: This package automates analysis workflow for TSA qPCR data. 
	Processing, analyzing, and visualizing data through both shiny 
	applications and command line exercises. Package aims to simplify 
	data analysis and offer front to end workflow from raw data to 
	multiple trial analysis.
